explains: v. （从外地）移居，移民；使移居入境

sentences.en: 10,000 people are expected to immigrate in the next two years.
sentences.cn: 在今后两年里，一万人有望移民。

sentences.en: They plan to immigrate to Finland next year.
sentences.cn: 他们计划明年移居芬兰。

sentences.en: He decided to immigrate to Australia to find work.
sentences.cn: 他决定移居到澳大利亚找个工作。
